Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是助手岩島京子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  京子  今天的气氛和以往有些不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  今晚的GillNay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在浦安市民游泳池的特别摄影场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,节目转型特别计划「满园春色GILLGILL游泳大会」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这节目怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法的嘛  这是社长接下工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用穿成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会吗  很可爱呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是这意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来介绍下特邀嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在  我是有田紫苑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要全力以赴喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  不行啊  这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羽泽  你看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑炭果然可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  她可是我们的秋叶原偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些杂鱼相比等级可不同啊  等级呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙居然看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得你与我通宵  这真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但必须尽快前去依露玛说的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报道研的调查还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马马虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室户前辈又那么靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老板你的店  还是没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那么又脏又乱  尽是些卖不出去的书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  和学生时代一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  对老板来说我还只是个孩童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(100,300)}（千のプラトー―資本主義と分裂症，\N原書名：MILLE PLATEAUX:(Capitalisme et schizophr'enie)）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是本好书啊  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an8}（スナックたまき：位于東京都大田区的Snack Bar）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  对不起呀  还在准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是来喝酒的  只是想来和你聊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,齐藤玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  库鲁库斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于走私拟态反应芯片  有些事情想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少装蒜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干…干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近  你有贩卖拟态反应芯片的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道  律师不在的场合我什么都不会说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我可没那时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快说！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近卖了6个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卖给谁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉  我还有约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  来干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是巴迪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴…巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说已经很久没有和你爸爸联系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我并不想和现在的老爸见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你协助了逃犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是阿留多人解放战线「伊兹达鲁塔」的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白说出「伊兹达鲁塔」这名字意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,标榜着阿留多人解放和主权获得的恐怖组织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还引发了中心塔恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸和那次恐怖爆炸无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前他已经脱离组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的打算退出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你清楚上面都在做些什么吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想和克丽丝蒂{\fn方正黑体_GBK}菈{\r}·利比联手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  这不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个利比大人身为阿留多人却位居科学所长官之位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即时如此  仍为我们站了出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  你是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是怕死罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能与此扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  中心塔就被炸毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后的对阿留多人迫害你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和老爸勉强得以从奥里奥特拉逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那家伙却又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  你只要稍微帮点忙就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是老交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝  我没打算要帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是误会什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是在求你协助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在恐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会就这么被抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候也会拉你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带还有那个没用的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  老爸是为了我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克和恐怖爆炸也有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃犯在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他们的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克就藏身在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  说明一下啊  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「伊兹达鲁塔」是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  是那个搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别出手  毕竟是关照过我们的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我得亲自去招待才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪放过我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她是联邦搜查官  一定会报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  莫斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  联邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和塔斯克接触过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还蛮喜欢这生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克那家伙  逃跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西贴着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然写我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  老爸  你暂时待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被那孩子抓住也不是件坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还在说这些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当初就别干什么亡命专家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  巴迪一定更加难受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会马上去找新房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之间你就老实待在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人  客房服务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客房服务？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错了吧  我可没有要过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  为了你预定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客房服务哦  塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来迎接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会耽搁多少时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想问你些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我们走一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没带武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉兹涅和迪安谢路两人被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:14:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遥测器上记录两人生命反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是怎么死的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  这我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人盯上我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像还知道我们的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你  塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你背后的是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会出卖客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是传说中的手臂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为「苍牙」的就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只是个阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别大惊小怪  擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过竟然可以伤到我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为阿留多人已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来  盯着我们的人就消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把尸体扔外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「伊兹达鲁塔」是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反联邦政府组织的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中心塔事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和功你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你有点奇怪啊  自从听了那些话以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁  小那塔鲁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,库鲁库斯  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是怎么了  出大事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克…你爸爸他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是预感吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸在神田经营这家店也已经有很长一段时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  那喝些饮料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  这个你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘乐酷啊  好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候老爸做给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这个  去那塔鲁家里经常玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你总是马上就捏坏  让老爸犯愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是法罗德先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是塔斯克的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是两人份吧  你妹妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个  快把这给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都需要一张新面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前问一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死老爸的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死塔斯克的是卡特尔他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能以璀璨的圣指起誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（圣指：即无名指，是人们使用频率最低的手指，\N由于不在日常生活中而只在特殊场合体现价值，故有「圣指」一称）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我以圣指起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  你把硫加解放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是从事研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说要使用它的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放…放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死在这里的人也会这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们连说出这话的时间都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个废墟正适合作为你们的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,法罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是从第十二个卵中孵化出来的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  我睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不过正因如此我才能和老爸单独对话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会抓住犯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶是巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连法罗德都被杀害的逃犯一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来认为犯人是偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是把偶引诱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  偶和功遇到了大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林  偶会怎么样呢
